The Celtic Stealth Warriors are back! And this time, they're bringing the big guns.

This is a full pack of heavy weapons to complement the full Celtic Stealth Army Epic Scale.

Included in this pack are -
5x Heavy weapons walkers each with 5 poses, with the following weapons:
 - Quad Cannon
 - Quad Laser Cannon
 - Laser Destroyer
 - AA missiles
 - Dronicide Bomb
5x Empty walker poses so you can add you own weapons to them
2x Walker Operators with AR and controllers
2x Gun Carriages each with 3 different poses, complete with Operator. Fitted with Quad Cannon or Laser Destroyer.
1x Quad Cannon Loader
5x Mortar teams in various poses
Some extra bits like ammo crates.

Supported files are included, completed test prints and painted up elements to follow.

Here we have a force of Celtic Stealth Warriors.

This set includes 57 items, broken down into -
 - 30 Troopers with Laser-carbines (15 poses duped between solid stocks and skeleton stocks)
- 10 Snipers (5 poses duped as above)
- 6 Scouts (3 aggressive 3 scouting)
- 3 Officers
- 5 Heavy MG teams

There is a mixture of hooded heads and unhooded with various hair stylings to represent the Celtic background, where no two people are the same and they don't follow uniform rules.

This set is included in the full Celtic Stealth Army set available here - https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/game/celtic-stealth-warriors-epic-scale

Update 1 - 5 man pre-supported models are inside the pack now, under the folder supported. Haven't supported individual models because... Does anyone print people in this scale individually?
